I seem to remember from my Studebaker collecting days
(still have a one ton truck at the Bus Co-op and a
bullet-nose sedan up in Placitas) that Ross made
steering boxes for Studebaker during the fifties, and
used a special lubricant.  I'll try to find more info
in the case that it's necessary.

